  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChatboxInput
    An event called when input is placed into the chatbox and sent
    ChatInput  
    ClientShutdown  
    ConfigChanged
    An event where a configuration entry has been modified.
    ConfigSync
    An event called when config is synced to disk/the server.

    Posted when an external plugin has been added, removed, or updated

    PrivateMessageInput  
    ProfileChanged
    Fired when the active ConfigProfile is changed
    RuneScapeProfileChanged
    Posted when the user switches to a different RuneScape save profile This might be because they logged into a different account, or hopped to/from a Beta/Tournament/DMM/Leagues world
    ScreenshotTaken
    Event fired when a screenshot is taken
    SessionClose
    An event where a new RuneLite account session has been closed, typically when logging out of the account.
    SessionOpen
    An event where a new RuneLite account session has been opened with the server.
    WorldsFetch
    Fired when the @{link net.runelite.client.game.WorldService} refreshes the world list
